name: Loje Nella (V)
Lore: 'Accountant. Descended from a species of cliff boring worms. Reluctant assistant to Mosep. Purposefully mismanages funds to obstruct Jabba''s nefarious activities.',
Text: 'May lose 2 Force to cancel Cold Feet if targeting Bo Shuda. While four or more cards are stacked on I Know That Laugh and/or your Objective, your Force drain bonuses may not be canceled. If you just Force drained with an alien, may activate 1 Force.',
